LoadModelFromFileWithMem(modelPath)¶

Function usage: Loads offline model data (adapted to the Ascend AI processor) from a file. The offline model file is the *.om file that adapts to the Ascend AI processor Input Args: model_path: str, path for storing the offline model file. The file name is contained in the path. Returns: model_id: model ID generated after the model is loaded.

ret: int, error code. 0 indicates success. Other values indicate failure.
